"windowDisplayName":"里美","body":"對耶……想起來當時的緊張了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":3,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":3,"voiceId":"event228-07-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"我還記得我們５人第一次一起\n奏響聲音那瞬間的興奮。自從登上舞台開始，\n我就一邊想著沙綾肯定會來，一邊彈吉他。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"event228-07-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"嗯嗯！當表演還剩一點點就要結束的時候，\n沙～綾就碰～地一聲打開體育館的大門進來了！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event228-07-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"呵呵，我那個時候還用跑的呢～\n我在聯絡走廊跟小里借鼓棒，\n完全沒練習就打鼓。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event228-07-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"２年級的時候，我們去接惠惠……\n跑了超遠……總之就是跑好跑滿。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event228-07-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"真的是服了那時的惠惠。呵呵呵。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":4,"voiceId":"event228-07-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":5}],"windowDisplayName":"有咲","body":"就是說啊，那個時候還真不容易啊～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":5,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":5,"voiceId":"event228-07-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":2}],"windowDisplayName":"多惠","body":"抱、抱歉。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":2,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":2,"voiceId":"event228-07-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":4}],"windowDisplayName":"沙綾","body":"呵呵，開玩笑的。感覺就好像很久遠以前發生的事喔。","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":4,"motionName":"nf0